<i>adverb</i>: 하긴 [하긴], 하기야 [하기야], 하기는 [하기는], 정작 [정ː작], 실제로 [실쩨로], 실제 [실쩨], 사실상 [사ː실쌍], 사실 [사ː실], 기실 [기실] <i>noun</i>: 사실 [사ː실] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하긴 [하긴]</dt><br>
<dd>in fact; in truth; indeed; actually</dd><br>
<dd>사실 말하자면.</dd><br>
<dd>To tell the truth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하기야 [하기야]</dt><br>
<dd>in fact; actually; in truth; as a matter of fact</dd><br>
<dd>사실 적당히 말하자면.</dd><br>
<dd>Indeed, roughly speaking.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하기는 [하기는]</dt><br>
<dd>in fact; in truth; indeed; actually</dd><br>
<dd>사실 말하자면.</dd><br>
<dd>To tell the truth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정작 [정ː작]</dt><br>
<dd>1. actually</dd><br>
<dd>실제로 어떤 일이 일어났을 때 생각했던 것과는 다르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner that is different to what one expected.</dd><br>
<dd>2. actually</dd><br>
<dd>실제로 어떤 일에 부닥쳐.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner that one faces a certain thing actually.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>실제로 [실쩨로]</dt><br>
<dd>actually</dd><br>
<dd>거짓이나 상상이 아니고 현실적으로. 정말로.</dd><br>
<dd>In reality, neither fictitiously nor imaginarily; really.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>실제 [실쩨]</dt><br>
<dd>really; actually</dd><br>
<dd>있는 그대로의 상태나 사실대로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state as it is or the fact as it is.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사실상 [사ː실쌍]</dt><br>
<dd>actually; as a matter of fact; de facto</dd><br>
<dd>실제에 있어서.</dd><br>
<dd>In reality.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사실 [사ː실]</dt><br>
<dd>actually; as a matter of fact; de facto</dd><br>
<dd>실제에 있어서.</dd><br>
<dd>In reality.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기실 [기실]</dt><br>
<dd>as a matter of fact; actually; in fact</dd><br>
<dd>실제에 있어서.</dd><br>
<dd>In reality.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사실 [사ː실]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fact</dd><br>
<dd>실제로 있었던 일이나 현재 일어나고 있는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An incident that actually happened or is in progress.</dd><br>
<dd>2. truth is</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않은 일을 솔직하게 말할 때 쓰는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An expression used to frankly tell someone something that is not seen nor known.</dd><br>
<dd>3. actually</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 말이 옳다고 강조할 때 쓰는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An expression used to stress that what one is saying is right.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>